{"tid":438322,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打都有甩頭髮問題⋯","createTime":"2017-10-16T22:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T13:18:49.000Z","uid":50767,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1c8bed5c8a9b59061ec10cfcd34b44787f9680","tid":438322,"uid":50767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T22:27:31.000Z","msg":"本身條界已經摩西分紅海咁撚闊<br />\n呢排仲好似甩得再勁啲<br />\n正常人一日甩100條係正常 我甩50已經好撚過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲要得廿歲頭 細個好撚厚好似中學開始變成咁<br />\n唔知應該做啲乜 <br />\n轉風筒唔知有用？想直上Dyson<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人試過按摩/食療/轉洗頭水等係work<br />\n救下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ee5fed13c2c4a5e68d5ecd76688f220d7313e9","tid":438322,"uid":55249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T22:35:38.000Z","msg":"光頭"},{"pid":"d86aaa6f4acc2299f5b0793d6f0c57c7d9ba3de4","tid":438322,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T22:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f1bd5f691fd4265cb9323f3e2f0e3a40a10158","tid":438322,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T22:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係關洗頭水事多<br />\n好似矽油問題 好似！"},{"pid":"40da2cd32dc02339fe7e4bdccd374dfef24387a5","tid":438322,"uid":109589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T22:54:53.000Z","msg":"唔好洗頭養一排"},{"pid":"f4416a05f2f1f89074980d0da43002844c2ac4e7","tid":438322,"uid":54020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T23:04:08.000Z","msg":"女性雄性禿  好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb6071847d3b147c92f6ac40d8a01f585bf4ccd","tid":438322,"uid":2546,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T00:18:20.000Z","msg":"屌自從d頭髮長咗之後 用手一梳就甩幾條幾條<br />\n夾頭髮又甩幾廿條 洗頭又甩 吹頭又甩 幾時變禿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110cc31babd5b954300259b0dc1dee0589e0c114","tid":438322,"uid":128127,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T00:32:04.000Z","msg":"啲頭髮甩到隨處何見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n梳頭唔係一條條甩 係一執執咁甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f52a2c2baed42bc51d991ff2938efd4821469d","tid":438322,"uid":74434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T00:41:14.000Z","msg":"我以前都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住就驚到瀨屎剪短左啲頭髮<br />\n而家又真係好番好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係啲頭髮留得差 唔多營養<br />\n兩三個月修一次會好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f38e6ef5c78c7d9bb2dfc8f4629cf7d005da169","tid":438322,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T00:43:20.000Z","msg":"剪晒佢"},{"pid":"854b507cf585a9b0ef4392bd112aeb6088afd398","tid":438322,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:36:45.000Z","msg":"剪短下會好少少既我諗<br />\n可能唔夠營養<br />\n中醫都有啲效,<br />\n同埋用無矽洗頭水啦<br />\n頭髮本身油既就唔好再用護髮素啦<br />\n洗完頭要即刻吹乾髮根, <br />\n唔好用咁熱既水洗頭"},{"pid":"32ccccaae7f0b64ac0bbbab537877423ec1d6dce","tid":438322,"uid":87946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"Dyson 無用啦<br />\n剪多啲早啲訓會好啲<br />\n利申無頭髮"},{"pid":"aec467f80a1486c01c997afc32ae53cee8aa9a94","tid":438322,"uid":50767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"唔捨得剪 由細到大都係長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但會去修修佢了"},{"pid":"fc76fbb20418c6ef954bbfa215b52cade62fb788","tid":438322,"uid":61635,"like":0,"disl